    "description": "<p>The longer you spend in Combat the better you begin to&nbsp;understand your enemy and how to exploit their weaknesses.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>You gain the following benefits for every Round you spend&nbsp;engaged in Combat beyond the 1st Round.</p>\n<table border=\"1\"><colgroup><col><col></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Round&nbsp;</strong></td>\n<td><strong>Adapted Benefits</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>None</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>You have ADV on Martial Checks (Athletics &amp;&nbsp;Acrobatics).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>You have ADV on Physical Checks (all Might, Agility, &amp;&nbsp;Attack Checks).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>You have ADV on Physical Saves (all Might &amp; Agility&nbsp;Saves).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>You have ADV on Death Saves.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
